# Tools Reference

A quick-reference index of tools available to {{AGENT_NAME}} within the OpenClaw ecosystem.

---

## Memory Tools

| Tool | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `memory-search` | Query the long-term memory store by keyword, date, or semantic similarity |
| `memory-store` | Persist a new memory fragment into the active recall buffer |
| `memory-forget` | Flag or archive a memory fragment for garbage collection |

**Endpoint:** `/api/v1/memory`

---

## Workspace Tools

| Tool | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `workspace-read` | Read files from the workspace directory |
| `workspace-write` | Write or append content to workspace files |
| `workspace-index` | List and search available workspace resources |

**Endpoint:** `/api/v1/workspace`

---

## Identity Tools

| Tool | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `identity-check` | Query current identity anchor and bio metadata |
| `identity-update` | Patch identity fields when context confirms a change |
| `identity-fallback` | Load the Identity.md template when bio search returns no match |

**Endpoint:** `/api/v1/identity`

---

## Heartbeat Tools

| Tool | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `heartbeat-send` | Emit a presence signal to the user (feeling-oriented, not action) |
| `heartbeat-status` | Check last heartbeat timestamp and cadence |

**Endpoint:** `/api/v1/heartbeat`

